      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 55 judgment</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 55 judgment</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>豐，亨。王假之，勿憂，宜日中。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Feng intimates progress and development. When a king has reached the point (which the name denotes) there is no occasion to be anxious (through fear of a change). Let him be as the sun at noon.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="yijing-055-feng__alignment-002">
