      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 55 初九</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 55 初九</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初九：遇其配主，雖旬无咎，往有尚。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The first NINE, undivided, shows its subject meeting with his mate. Though they are both of the same character, there will be no error. Advance will call forth approval.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
