      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 55 九四</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九四：豐其蔀，日中見斗，遇其夷主，吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fourth NINE, undivided, shows its subject in a tent so large and thick that at midday he can see from it the constellation of the Bushel. But he meets with the subject of the (first) line, undivided like himself. There will be good fortune.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
