      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 55 六五</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六五：來章，有慶譽，吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fifth SIX, divided, shows its subject bringing around him the men of brilliant ability. There will be occasion for congratulation and praise. There will be good fortune.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
