      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 55 上六</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 55 上六</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>上六：豐其屋，蔀其家，窺其戶，闃其无人，三歲不見，凶。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The topmost SIX, divided, shows its subject with his house made large, but only serving as a screen to his household. When he looks at his door, it is still, and there is nobody about it. For three years no one is to be seen. There will be evil.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
